content: I'm planning to rent a bike and explore the Swamp Rabbit Trail, and maybe even stop by Falls Park for a picnic. It sounds like a great way to get some exercise and enjoy the scenery. Thanks for the recommendations! By the way, I was thinking about my own goals and aspirations, and I realized that I've been putting off learning a new skill for too long. Do you think Greenville has any resources for learning a new language or taking online courses during my trip?
